  "system": {
    "fuid": "fafnir",
    "summary": {
      "value": "The invulnerable chtonic dragon, who guards legendary treasures."
    },
    "featureType": "projectfu.arcanum",
    "data": {
      "merge": "<h3>Scales of the Ardent Sovereign</h3><p>You gain Resistance to <strong>fire</strong> damage. Additionally, as long as you are <strong>not in Crisis</strong>, you also gain Resistance to <strong>physical</strong> damage.</p><p>All damage you deal becomes <strong>fire</strong>, its type cannot change, and it ignores Resistances; as long as you are in <strong>Crisis</strong>, it also ignores Immunities.</p><p>When you deal damage to <strong>only one creature</strong> with a spell, you deal 10 extra damage.</p>",
      "pulse": "",
      "dismiss": "<h3>Molten Gold</h3><p>You deal 20 <strong>fire</strong> damage to every enemy you can see, or 30 <strong>fire</strong> damage if you are in <strong>Crisis</strong>; this damage ignores Immunities and Resistances. Then, you and every ally present on the scene regain 2 Inventory Points for every enemy reduced to 0 Hit Points by this damage.</p><hr><p><strong>Enemies Suffer:</strong> @DMG[&step(20,30,40)+10*(1-min(1,floor(max($hp-1,0)/floor($mhp/2)))) fire|ingore-resistances,ignore-immunities|]{20/30 Fire}<br><strong>You & Allies Gain:</strong> @GAIN[2 ip]</p>",
      "domains": "fire, protection, wealth"
    },
    "source": "FUBC34"
  },
